        Send the value of the encoder to the dashboard for displaying
        Parameters:
        distance - Distance the encoder has traveled (in inches)
        linearSpeed - Linear speed of the encoder (in ft/s)
        wheelDiameter - Diameter of the wheel (used to calculate RPM)
        name - Name of the encoder to display on the dashboard
        mod1 - Module of the first PWM (1 or 2)
        slot1 - Slot of the first PWM (1 through 14)

        slot2 - Slot of the second PWM (1 through 14)
